Sentencas: Compared with planar SOFCs, tubular SOFCs have the advantages of facile sealing and easy scale up.

Sentencas: In this study, a tubular anode-supported thin-film YSZ electrolyte SOFC was successfully fabricated by extrusion of the anode substrate in combination with wet powder spraying of the electrolyte layer.
